{"tid":420223,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大雨中既的士司機真係好好人","createTime":"2017-10-01T08:23:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-02T12:24:41.000Z","uid":34215,"like":1367,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"1eb1959ef13c1dc178ac8c5dc236c8c0f9937190","tid":420223,"uid":34215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T08:23:26.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母死老虔婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開左車之後已經用的士司機個啲手機channel同佢同事係咁傾計，係到嫌路程短，隔涉，賺得唔夠多<br />\n我聽到心諗唉，算啦，咁的士司機都係想賺多啲姐<br />\n好啦<br />\n我一早叫佢入埋閘<br />\n到左閘口竟然同我講<br />\n我唔入閘架啦，又要拍卡會搞到我濕晒，好易會病，你係呢度落<br />\n戇撚柒鳩鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搭得的士就係唔想淋雨，但又唔敢屌佢<br />\n我同佢講，咁我都係會淋雨架姐，佢竟然答我你返屋企可以沖涼呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌柒佢，點都要入埋閘先肯落車<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老虔婆身子弱，自己淋下雨冇咩既"},{"pid":"e67ab4d5b64711b0f9faf7370f86aa4dd84637f0","tid":420223,"uid":36383,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T08:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我老豆早排又見到唔入閘嘅的士司機，屌到佢仆街"},{"pid":"26514a7e5c7085463b0471a6828a75bba679c055","tid":420223,"uid":34215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T08:25:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌佢老母死老虔婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開左車之後已經用的士司機個啲手機channel同佢同事係咁傾計，係到嫌路程短，隔涉，賺得唔夠多<br />\n我聽到心諗唉，算啦，咁的士司機都係想賺多啲姐<br />\n好啦<br />\n我一早叫佢入埋閘<br />\n到左閘口竟然同我講<br />\n我唔入閘架啦，又要拍卡會搞到我濕晒，好易會病，你係呢度落<br />\n戇撚柒鳩鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搭得的士就係唔想淋雨，但又唔敢屌佢<br /